1
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:25,280
Mom.

2
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,000
Xingxing is back.

3
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:29,440
Come sit.

4
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:32,440
Dad picked me up first.

5
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,440
That's nice.

6
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:36,400
Did you have fun at school?

7
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:37,520
Yes.

8
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:40,080
Ms. Hudie took us to slide

9
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,720
on a huge slide.

10
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:43,120
A huge slide.

11
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,920
Did you miss Mom?

12
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,880
Yes.

13
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,479
By the way, Mom,

14
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,120
Ms. Hudie said

15
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:55,920
there will be a welcome party for new students next week.

16
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,720
The parents

17
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:59,520
have to perform together.

18
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:02,120
What do you want me to perform?

19
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,520
Dance.

20
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:06,720
Like a prince and a princess,

21
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:08,520
spinning around.

22
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:11,120
But Xingxing, you know,

23
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:13,920
Mom is only good at punching bad guys.

24
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:15,520
You want Mommy to dance?

25
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:18,079
Mommy really doesn't know how.

26
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,680
If you don't know how,

27
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,840
I'll teach you.

28
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:21,960
Stop it.

29
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,960
When I was in school,

30
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,840
I had two left feet even doing aerobics.

31
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:27,040
So you want to disappoint Little Star?

32
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,280
What are you talking about?

33
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,800
How can we disappoint our kid?

34
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,860
Tell me, how do you want to torture me?

35
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,800
How do I learn this?

36
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:47,780
Put your left hand on my shoulder.

37
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,050
Put your right hand in mine.

38
00:02:52,079 --> 00:02:52,920
You...

39
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,610
The waltz requires core strength.

40
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,930
If I can't find the right position,

41
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,740
how can I lead you in a spin?

42
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,660
You're so good at this.

43
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:03,520
How many people have you taught?

44
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:06,100
Definitely not as many men as you've thrown.

45
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,720
Step with your left foot.

46
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:12,520
Follow with your right foot.

47
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,720
I... I'm sorry.

48
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:32,760
No, no.

49
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,440
I need to process this myself.

50
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:36,640
Don't you have work to do at the company?

51
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,640
Go ahead.

52
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,579
Then I'll try to finish early,

53
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,200
come back,

54
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:46,040
and check your homework.

55
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:12,850
You took such ugly photos of us, Xingxing.

56
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,560
Look at you.

57
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,720
What kind of angle is this?

58
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,079
This one is okay.

59
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,720
I stepped on your dad's foot in this one.

60
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:24,320
There's a surprise in the next ones.

61
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:28,840
Mom, I've seen this granny before.

62
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,800
Where did you see her?

63
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,840
When I was in the orphanage,

64
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:37,080
Granny came to celebrate my birthday once.

65
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,960
She brought a strawberry cake,

66
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:42,440
and said I looked like her daughter when she was little.

67
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:45,480
The original host's mother knew of Xiaoxingxing's existence.

68
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,680
She even went to the orphanage

69
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,480
to celebrate Xiaoxingxing's birthday.

70
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,840
When is your birthday?

71
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,560
February 10th.

72
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,600
You are so impatient.

73
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:30,360
Don't you know to take things slowly?

74
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,820
How much longer do I have to endure this, Mom?

75
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:35,600
Everyone in this company,

76
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:38,000
except for Dad, revolves around my older brother.

77
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,730
Does anyone even care about me?

78
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,580
You have the nerve to say that.

79
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,600
If you had listened to me

80
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,860
and intercepted Shen Zhixia,

81
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:48,200
would we be in this situation now?

82
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:51,080
Your good brother got the support of the Shen family.

83
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:51,880
Mom.

84
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:55,440
Shen Zhixia is such a boring woman.

85
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:57,040
I spent so much effort coaxing her.

86
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,280
I tried my best.

87
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:00,600
That old man, Shen Jingyao,

88
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,760
is dead set on clinging to my older brother.

89
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:02,960
What else could I do?

90
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,560
You sure had a way.

91
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,640
You couldn't wait

92
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:09,200
to replace the suppliers with your own people.

93
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:11,600
You were so afraid others wouldn't see your intentions,

94
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,720
my good son.

95
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,640
If Dad hadn't been dragging his feet

96
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,720
and refusing to finalize the inheritance,

97
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,850
would I have had to take such a big risk?

98
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,960
Not finalizing it has its own benefits.

99
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:23,760
Your dad is getting old,

100
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:27,120
and his health is deteriorating by the day.

101
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,890
If worse comes to worst,

102
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:32,220
we'll find an opportunity

103
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,360
and give him a push.

104
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,720
Make a move on Dad?

105
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,659
The old man hasn't made a will,

106
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:48,720
so half of the property should rightfully be mine.

107
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,400
The remaining half,

108
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:53,080
you and Lu Jingheng can split.

109
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,760
What about the company, Mom?

110
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:04,560
Those old foxes are naturally profit-driven.

111
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:08,360
They'll follow whoever gives them the most benefits.

112
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:12,000
By then, you and Lu Jingheng will be evenly matched.

113
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,720
I don't believe it.

114
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:16,200
In such a big company,

115
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:18,080
can he call the shots alone?

116
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,520
Jingxi.

117
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,520
Listen to Mom.

118
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,760
No matter what you hear outside,

119
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:29,920
you are not allowed to go out.

120
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,920
Did you hear me?

121
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,480
Shen Zhixia, stop.

122
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,760
Shen Zhixia.

123
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,640
About you and Jingxi,

124
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:53,700
you don't want others to know, right?

125
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,760
Let's make a deal.

126
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,520
Give me the phone.

127
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:03,280
I won't say a word about you and Jingxi.

128
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,200
Give it to me.

129
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:12,000
Give me the phone.

130
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,400
Give it to me.

131
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,760
I was wondering

132
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:34,360
why I came back in time covered in injuries.

133
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,679
Shen Jingyao is old,

134
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:39,360
so how could he have beaten me like this?

135
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,120
It turns out

136
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,320
I fell at this time.

137
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:52,540
Su Manyun thought the dead tell no tales,

138
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:55,050
but she didn't expect this.

139
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,200
The original owner's phone

140
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:59,600
automatically backed up to the cloud.

141
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:01,760
I was wondering

142
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:04,760
why she was so guarded against me when we first met.

143
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:08,600
It seems it's not just because Lu Jingxi wants to seize power,

144
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,650
It has nothing to do with me.

145
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,920
but she's also afraid I'll bring up the past

146
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:17,320
and expose her secret.

147
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,200
See for yourself.

148
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:52,240
Take a good look.

149
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,840
The two ingrates I raised.

150
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:03,000
How did I ever wrong you?

151
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,200
For a little family fortune,

152
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:07,840
you actually hoped I would die.

153
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:10,680
All these years,

154
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:14,200
you've put on quite an act.

155
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:17,160
How could you be at peace

156
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:18,560
staying by my side

157
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,880
and hoping for me to die every day?

158
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,680
I did complain.

159
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:30,610
But did I really want to take your life?

160
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,600
For so many years,

161
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:33,680
I have served you.

162
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:36,210
Even if I don't have merits, I've worked hard.

163
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:39,410
But you only care about your precious eldest son.

164
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,640
What are Jingxi and I to you?

165
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:43,480
Nonsense.

166
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:47,840
When have I ever mistreated you?

167
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:52,560
Still stubborn even at death's door.

168
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,880
You treacherous wretch.

169
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,400
Get out.

170
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,600
Get out, all of you.

171
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,560
Fine, we'll leave.

172
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:04,840
But I just can't accept this.

173
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:09,600
How is my son worse than him?

174
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:12,360
Why isn't he good enough for you?

175
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:15,040
You can despise me.

176
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,680
I have nothing to say.

177
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:20,280
Jingxi is your own son.

178
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:22,360
Even a tiger doesn't eat its cubs.

179
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:25,960
Are you trying to make him homeless?

180
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,520
Dad.

181
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:32,200
Mom is just talking nonsense because she's angry.

182
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:36,200
Have you forgotten how good Mom has been to you all these years?

183
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:38,280
You can't just listen to my brother and sister-in-law

184
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,960
and drive us to a dead end.

185
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:46,040
Don't give me that.

186
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:51,200
Okay, I'll give you one more chance.

187
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:54,400
Confess everything in detail.

188
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,600
What have you been doing

189
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,880
in the company lately?

190
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:01,610
Which board members did you bribe?

191
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:02,600
Speak.

192
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:11,090
You won't speak?

193
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:16,800
Fine, I will investigate it myself.

194
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:19,400
Once I find out the truth,

195
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,880
I will settle the score with you.

196
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:23,720
Men!

197
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:28,520
Sir.

198
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:31,000
Keep them under watch.

199
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,840
Without my permission,

200
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:36,120
they are not allowed to take a single step outside.

201
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:36,920
Yes.

202
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:40,280
Madam, Second Young Master.

203
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,200
Pardon me.

204
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,160
Walk by yourself.

205
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,080
Bye-bye.

